      <ul>
        <li>Reduce cost by right sizing and optimizing your AWS environment using granular data from Datadog</li>
	<li>Automate policies and governance to reduce risk</li>
	<li>Tackle Reserved Instances with confidence using CloudHealth’s analysis and automation</li>
	<li>Visualize your assets across clouds aligned to line of business</li>
